title: Tweeting Through It
description: After figuring out if they're the last people on earth, Katie and Ashley dive into NFL Week 3. They get into Antonio Brown's new college courses (17:55), Gardner Minshew the urban legend (23:50), and Jay's first Ravens game (37:20). Later, there's a College Football Update (1:01:20), a baseball hero who has never been to the gym (1:10:55), and some erotic news of the week (1:11:38).
